full_title: Heart Of A Woman by Summer Walker
title: Heart Of A Woman

description.plain:
“Heart of a Woman” is the lead single from Summer Walker’s third studio album, Finally Over It. The song was first teased by Walker on August 3, 2024, when she posted a snippet across her social media accounts.

On October 11, 2024, a link to pre-save the song was shared, accompanied by a visual that further heightened anticipation for the release.

On October 23, Summer officially announced the song’s release date to be the following Friday, October 25.
